Package: monarchr
Type: Package
Title: Interface to Monarch Initiative API for Phenotype Ontology and Genotype
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given="Charles C", family="Carey", email = "charlieccarey@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
             person("Ted", "Laderas", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <charlieccarey@gmail.com>
Description: The Monarch Initiative integrates and manages ontologies,
    phenotypes, genetics and genotypes across many species from many 
    resources. The monarchr package uses the monarch web API to retrieve 
    that information into an R environment.
